data.description: Situated in the heart of Hopewell Junction on just under 1.5 acres you will find this charming, meticulously maintained Cape Cod style home. As you approach the home up the private driveway, you are greeted by the well-kept landscaping and mature foliage that graces the property. Upon entering the home, you are greeted by an abundance of natural light gleaming off the beautiful hardwood floors. Imagine yourself preparing a meal in the spacious eat-in kitchen, with a large kitchen island at it's center, and stainless steel appliances throughout. The first floor den/office provides the ideal private work from home space for all your professional needs. Take in the private backyard from the newly redone back deck. Additionally on the first floor you will find a beautifully updated full bathroom, as well as a spacious first floor bedroom. Upstairs you will find the large primary bedroom with walk in closet, as well as two additional bedrooms, and a second newly renovated full bathroom. Additional features include the attached two car garage, and large basement perfect for all your storage needs. Just seconds from the Taconic State Parkway, this home is conveniently located close to shopping, restaurants, schools, I-84 and Metro-North Rail Line. This spectacular home is truly one you do not want to miss, call to schedule your appointment today!
